reviewText: This is more along the lines of WWE produced Diva DVDs than the original Vixxen videos that showcased Missy Hyatt and "friends".  It's not horrible by any means but if you were expecting something more "revealing" than this isn't for you.  I could've sworn a product description stated matches involving the women on this DVD would be included, but alas- there are none.

The other wrestling vixens shows hot women doing strip shows to the buff! This piece of fluff has some girls only in swimsuits and little outfits! Skip it and order the others if you can find them stll in print!
